{"about_the_game":"<strong> DESTROY ALL THE GODS! </strong><br><br>The body of the thunder god has been taken over by the most cunning god of the universe. Find the gods hidden in different realms and destroy them all until you are the only god left standing!<br><br><strong> YOU'RE THE VERY RAGNAROK ITSELF </strong><br><br>There's no hero's tale here. On the contrary, you will be the nightmare of heroes! Develop your strategy and unleash the cosmic calamity. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2462570/extras/thorSteam.gif?t=1716821730\" /><br><br><strong> EVERY DEFEAT IS A NEW BEGINNING </strong><br><br>Giving up is not in the nature of the thunder god. Each time you are defeated, warp time and start over with what you've gained. Embark on your next journey more experienced and powerful.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2462570/extras/Ads\u0131z__600_x_338_piksel___1_.gif?t=1716821730\" /><br><br><strong>CUSTOMIZE YOUR CHARACTER TO FIT YOUR STRATEGY</strong><br><br>Various weapons, armors, abilities, allies, and more have been specifically designed for you to develop your own strategy. Choose what suits you best and develop it permanently. You are free to choose whatever you want before you start fighting.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2462570/extras/Ads\u0131z__600_x_338_piksel_.gif?t=1716821730\" /><br><br><strong>REALMS, CHARACTERS, AND CREATURES TO DISCOVER</strong><br><br>With dynamic and voiced dialogues, realms offering different experiences and challenges, a vast bestiary, and dozens of characters you will get to know, Nine Realms presents a new universe and a deep story that tackles Norse Mythology in a different reality, waiting for you to discover.<br><br><strong>FATE BOWS BEFORE THE INEVITABLE</strong><br><br>Enjoy being the thunder god with detailed leveling and development systems, an immersive story, and realistic graphic quality! Remember, there are no rules here, you are here only to destroy.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Draugr Slayer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2462570/bcabff14c2bea85c0386313375bd8265f32b03e3.jpg"},{"name":"Elemental Slayer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2462570/0fb00e3a2567285a629f2c916c6e996133a7c055.jpg"},{"name":"Valhalla Soldier is Now Home!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2462570/729415c3970da4b669db4b7c865141a7d2e0df40.jpg"},{"name":"Soldier Slayer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2462570/b3cee258465d9bedda11b3cf8d28cc2e1755aea5.jpg"},{"name":"End of Justice","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2462570/df9758a72e80d890f010f37ed055b756c78a99e5.jpg"},{"name":"Valhalla Reaper is Home Too!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2462570/9ac8547562c1a1b7a0ec5db4f599b698d899043a.jpg"},{"name":"Reaper Slayer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2462570/1216cc07534903711ad27bc319623dc59c459fa0.jpg"},{"name":" The Goddess of Beauty is No Longer Beautiful... ","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2462570/17f2b07f9d1be30dcc94e9592f4add8755503152.jpg"},{"name":"Just Getting Warmed Up!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2462570/92e77f8a88a2ca88776812fda364ed991f223ec1.jpg"},{"name":"Oh, Level Up again! Keepin\u2019 it Up!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2462570/4645357868e5c7e091001f13a42b7745ccd6bab5.jpg"}],"total":19},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2462570/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1716821730","backgr